@startuml
title TraceLeft System - Deployment and Control Flow

actor User
participant "CLI Interface\n(Cobra)" as CLI
participant "Command Processor" as CMD
participant "gotext Tool" as Gotext
participant "Text Processing\nLayer" as TextProc
participant "Unicode Normalizer\n(norm)" as Norm
participant "Collation Engine\n(collate)" as Collate
participant "IDNA Processor" as IDNA
participant "eBPF Manager\n(gobpf)" as eBPF
participant "System Call\nInterface" as SysCall
participant "Unix/Windows\nAPI Layer" as OS
participant "Kernel" as Kernel
participant "YAML Config\nProcessor" as YAML
participant "LRU Cache" as Cache
participant "File System\nWatcher" as FSWatch

== System Initialization ==
User -> CLI: Execute traceleft command
activate CLI
CLI -> CMD: Parse command and flags
activate CMD
CMD -> YAML: Load configuration
activate YAML
YAML --> CMD: Return config data
deactivate YAML
CMD -> Cache: Initialize LRU cache
activate Cache
Cache --> CMD: Cache ready
deactivate Cache

== eBPF Program Deployment ==
CMD -> eBPF: Load eBPF program
activate eBPF
eBPF -> SysCall: Request BPF filesystem access
activate SysCall
SysCall -> OS: System call (bpf)
activate OS
OS -> Kernel: Load eBPF program
activate Kernel
Kernel --> OS: Program loaded
deactivate Kernel
OS --> SysCall: Success
deactivate OS
SysCall --> eBPF: Program handle
deactivate SysCall
eBPF -> eBPF: Attach to kprobes/tracepoints
eBPF --> CMD: eBPF ready
deactivate eBPF

== File System Monitoring Setup ==
CMD -> FSWatch: Initialize file watcher
activate FSWatch
FSWatch -> OS: Register inotify/ReadDirectoryChangesW
activate OS
OS --> FSWatch: Watch descriptor
deactivate OS
FSWatch --> CMD: Watcher active
deactivate FSWatch

== Text Processing Pipeline ==
User -> CLI: Input internationalized text
CLI -> CMD: Process text command
CMD -> Gotext: Extract translatable strings
activate Gotext
Gotext -> TextProc: Analyze text structure
activate TextProc
TextProc -> Norm: Normalize Unicode (NFC/NFD)
activate Norm
Norm -> Norm: Lookup sparse trie tables
Norm -> Norm: Apply combining classes
Norm --> TextProc: Normalized text
deactivate Norm

TextProc -> IDNA: Process domain names
activate IDNA
IDNA -> IDNA: Map Unicode to ASCII (UTS #46)
IDNA -> IDNA: Validate Bidi rules
IDNA -> IDNA: Trie-based rune lookup
IDNA --> TextProc: Processed domains
deactivate IDNA

TextProc -> Collate: Sort/compare strings
activate Collate
Collate -> Collate: Load CLDR tables
Collate -> Collate: Apply locale rules
Collate -> Collate: Sparse trie compression
Collate --> TextProc: Sorted results
deactivate Collate

TextProc --> Gotext: Processed text
deactivate TextProc
Gotext -> Gotext: Generate message packages
Gotext --> CMD: Localized output
deactivate Gotext

== Runtime Tracing and Monitoring ==
CMD -> eBPF: Start event collection
activate eBPF
loop Continuous Monitoring
    Kernel -> eBPF: Kernel event (kprobe/tracepoint)
    activate Kernel
    eBPF -> Cache: Check event cache
    activate Cache
    Cache --> eBPF: Cache hit/miss
    deactivate Cache

    alt Cache miss
        eBPF -> TextProc: Process event data
        activate TextProc
        TextProc -> Norm: Normalize event strings
        activate Norm
        Norm --> TextProc: Normalized data
        deactivate Norm
        TextProc --> eBPF: Processed event
        deactivate TextProc
        eBPF -> Cache: Store in cache
        activate Cache
        Cache --> eBPF: Cached
        deactivate Cache
    end

    eBPF --> CMD: Event data
    deactivate Kernel
end
deactivate eBPF

== File System Event Handling ==
FSWatch -> CMD: File change detected
activate FSWatch
activate CMD
CMD -> YAML: Reload configuration
activate YAML
YAML --> CMD: Updated config
deactivate YAML
CMD -> eBPF: Reconfigure eBPF programs
activate eBPF
eBPF -> SysCall: Update program
activate SysCall
SysCall -> OS: System call
activate OS
OS -> Kernel: Update filters
activate Kernel
Kernel --> OS: Updated
deactivate Kernel
OS --> SysCall: Success
deactivate OS
SysCall --> eBPF: Updated
deactivate SysCall
eBPF --> CMD: Reconfigured
deactivate eBPF
CMD --> FSWatch: Handled
deactivate CMD
deactivate FSWatch

== Output Generation ==
CMD -> CLI: Format trace output
CLI -> TextProc: Apply locale formatting
activate TextProc
TextProc -> Collate: Sort trace entries
activate Collate
Collate --> TextProc: Sorted entries
deactivate Collate
TextProc --> CLI: Formatted output
deactivate TextProc
CLI --> User: Display results
deactivate CMD
deactivate CLI

== System Cleanup ==
User -> CLI: Terminate command
activate CLI
CLI -> CMD: Shutdown signal
activate CMD
CMD -> eBPF: Detach eBPF programs
activate eBPF
eBPF -> SysCall: Close BPF handles
activate SysCall
SysCall -> OS: Release resources
activate OS
OS -> Kernel: Unload programs
activate Kernel
Kernel --> OS: Unloaded
deactivate Kernel
OS --> SysCall: Released
deactivate OS
SysCall --> eBPF: Closed
deactivate SysCall
eBPF --> CMD: Detached
deactivate eBPF

CMD -> FSWatch: Stop file watcher
activate FSWatch
FSWatch -> OS: Unregister watches
activate OS
OS --> FSWatch: Stopped
deactivate OS
FSWatch --> CMD: Stopped
deactivate FSWatch

CMD -> Cache: Cleanup cache
activate Cache
Cache --> CMD: Cleared
deactivate Cache

CMD --> CLI: Cleanup complete
deactivate CMD
CLI --> User: Exit
deactivate CLI

@enduml
